Package: ClinSim
Title: Sample Size Checking by Simulatin
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Anushka", "Jitendra", , "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for checking comparing sample size calculations using simulation. 
    Provides an approach to the two sample Wilcoxon rank sum test, compares Noether 
    and TrialSize approximations, estimates achieved power through Monte Carlo simulation 
    and inlcudes tools for plotting power and sample size curves across varying effect sizes.
    Also provides simulation-based validation for two-samplemean (t-test) sample size calculations.
